。<br />\n<br />\n24個月合約，計劃已包留言信箱、來電轉駁、來電顯示、來電待接及電話會議，並可使用香港寬頻本地 Wifi 網絡。<br />\n<br />\n優惠期內送MyTV Super 基本版流動應用程式服務24個月。（原價每年$380）<br />\n<br />\n歡迎攜號轉台，需以信用卡自動轉賬<br />\n<br />\n想取得優惠月費回贈，請登入以下網址連結：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://r.hkbn.net/S/SSHKBN10017\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fr.hkbn.net%2FS%2FSSHKBN10017&d=8WwZ2LD91TkRcLKoFnA1pJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=42780af1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://r.hkbn.net/S/SSHKBN10017</a><br />\n<br />\n月費回贈會在開始使用服務後存入閣下香港寬頻賬戶內，用作扣減月費之用。<br />\n<br />\n如果登記後出現問題，香港寬頻會專人聯絡閣下。"},{"pid":"4f078ab3ce3d030e3452290a49e0d3291c009119","tid":365583,"uid":138087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T11:27:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2af26e9082281d12d38e090d75de6725c9f3ffb7","tid":365583,"uid":138472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T12:05:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5830bd0c78e32b2493bfd6d0a66d425cafe8049a","tid":365583,"uid":136346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T13:45:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f0d3928714a99df8103f6e0c802dc453dbb89985","tid":365583,"uid":136717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T17:25:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"49986af37f1fdc5e4a5ebe5d2e3fccd79d213a81","tid":365583,"uid":138472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T19:20:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6780f2eaf30a2d294b3278f499500673cb00b8fe","tid":365583,"uid":138514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T21:03:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dbec13d823d6d809c69bc9ede999daa8caf5bb47","tid":365583,"uid":130101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T22:58:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8019c116b8c0f5f91a5f324da225aec6e284de55","tid":365583,"uid":138472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T02:24:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eaffb1dbb29e3a23dd7933b54